com.analog.lyric.dimple.options

Class DimpleOptionRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.analog.lyric.options.OptionRegistry
      • com.analog.lyric.dimple.options.DimpleOptionRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<IOptionKey<?>>

    public final class DimpleOptionRegistry
extends OptionRegistry
    Registry of option keys for known dimple options.

    This is used primarily for looking up option keys by name from dynamic language front-ends (e.g. MATLAB). Java users should instead directly use the key objects.

    Includes options from the following classes:

    General options
    • DimpleOptions
    • SolverOptions
    Solver-specific options
    • BPOptions
    • GibbsOptions
    • JunctionTreeOptions
    • LPOptions
    • MinSumOptions
    • ParticleBPOptions
    • SumProductOptions
    Proposal kernels options
    • NormalProposalKernel
    • CircularNormalProposalKernel
    Sampler options
    • MHSampler
    • SliceSampler
    Additional options can be added to the registry using addFromClasses.

    Instances of this class should be obtained from DimpleEnvironment.optionRegistry().
